Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 05 of Head MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button

When I select 'Epidural hematoma' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Median' checkbox is enabled

And 'Frontal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Temporal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Parietal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Occipital' checkbox is enabled
And 'Infratentorial' checkbox is enabled

And 'Size' input field is enabled
And 'Durale attachment exceeded' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sutures not exceeded' checkbox is enabled
And 'Displaced dura between EDH and brain' checkbox is enabled

And 'Biconvex' checkbox is enabled

And 'Skull fracture' checkbox is enabled
And 'Contrecoup SDH' checkbox is enabled
And 'Adjacent contusion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Concomitant cerebrospinal fluid congestion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Associated infarction' checkbox is enabled

When I enter 1 in 'Size' input field
Then the value is accepted
And '2nd plane' input field is enabled

When I enter 250 in 'Size' input field
Then the value is accepted
And '2nd plane' input field is enabled

When I enter 1 in '2nd plane' input field
Then the value is accepted
And '3rd plane' input field is enabled

When I enter 250 in '2nd plane' input field
Then the value is accepted
And '3rd plane' input field is enabled

When I enter 1 in '3rd plane' input field
Then the value is accepted

When I enter 250 in '3rd plane' input field
Then the value is accepted

